    <p><!--Based on https://wiki.hpcloud.net/display/HCG/.Helion+CG+1.1+GA+Patch+Instructions--></p>
    <section>
      <p>After deploying the HP OpenStack cloud, On each compute node, update the following lines in
        the /etc/default/nuage-metadata-agent to reflect:</p>
      <p> </p>
      <p>1. Keystone URL to have suffix /v2.0</p>
      <p> </p>
      <p># NOVA_OS_AUTH_URL=http://&lt;ip_address&gt;:5000/v2.0</p>
      <p># NOVA_OS_AUTH_URL=http://10.30.3.103:35357</p>
      <p>NOVA_OS_AUTH_URL=http://10.30.3.103:5000/v2.0</p>
      <p> </p>
      <p>2. Nova api endpoint type need to be internalURL </p>
      <p> </p>
      <p># NOVA_API_ENDPOINT_TYPE: one of publicURL, internalURL, adminURL </p>
      <p># NOVA_API_ENDPOINT_TYPE=publicURL </p>
      <p>NOVA_API_ENDPOINT_TYPE=internalURL</p>
      <p> </p>
      <p> </p>
    </section>
